About Us
The Ultimate Tracking's functions: - Track vehicles' paths at different times - Observe multiple vehicles at the same time - Share your current location to others - Wake you up if you travel by public transportation
More information about The Ultimate Tracking: - We needed to make threads on Microsoft Forum to find the solutions to GMAP problems. - Our separate apps were incompatible at first, so we stayed at Pha and Kiet's house to fix the issue. - Ngan had to use Linh's computer via Team Viewer to finish the project because her computer was so weak. - Ngoc also had to use Phong's computer :)))
Team Avogadro[i1821]: 1. Le Tan Phong (Phong Le Odyssey) 2. Le Minh Anh Ngoc (Anh Ngot) 3. Huynh Bao Ngan (Ngan Huynh)
